| GPS tracks | Reconstruct route movement and stop locations |
| Raw NMEA data | Validate location movement and timing |
| Route history | Identify saved, repeated, or deleted navigation routes |
| Destinations | Map recurring operational locations |
| Bluetooth paired devices | Identify recurring nearby devices and convoy correlation |
| Keyfob/cargo-door logs | Identify loading and transfer windows |
| Suspension logs | Measure outbound and return load differences |
| OBD snapshots | Compare speed, throttle, RPM, and load behavior |
| DTC logs | Identify mechanical overload fault patterns |
| EDR events | Identify emergency braking and checkpoint/intercept events |
| Deleted messages | Recover instructions, warnings, cover story, and concealment behavior |
| Call logs and contacts | Support actor and role mapping |
| POI searches | Identify route, border, or deletion-related search behavior |
| USB/system events | Identify export or deletion attempts |
| Recovered images and receipts | Corroborate movement, stops, fuel events, tolls, manifests, and final-run activity |

